elements.expression: CASE  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('am', 'ac','om') THEN 'Livre imprimé'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='as' THEN 'Revue imprimée'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN('gm','gn','gs') THEN 'DVD'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='bm' THEN 'Manuscrit'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('jm', 'im' ,'jn') THEN 'CD'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='km' THEN 'Image fixe'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='em' THEN 'Carte imprimée'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='cm' THEN 'Partition imprimée'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('mm','ms') THEN 'Document multimedia multisupport'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='lm' THEN 'Document électronique'  ELSE 'Autre document' END
elements.viewExpression: CASE  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('am', 'ac','om') THEN 'Livre imprimé'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='as' THEN 'Revue imprimée'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN('gm','gn','gs') THEN 'DVD'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='bm' THEN 'Manuscrit'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('jm', 'im' ,'jn') THEN 'CD'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='km' THEN 'Image fixe'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='em' THEN 'Carte imprimée'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='cm' THEN 'Partition imprimée'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2) IN ('mm','ms') THEN 'Document multimedia multisupport'  WHEN SUBSTRING(ExtractValue(#agkf,'//leader'), 7, 2)='lm' THEN 'Document électronique'  ELSE 'Autre document' END

CASE substring(ExtractValue(#agkf,'//leader'),7,1)  WHEN 'a' THEN 'Doc textuel'  WHEN 'b' THEN 'Doc textuel manuscrit' WHEN 'c' THEN 'Partition' WHEN 'd' THEN 'Partition manuscrite' WHEN 'e' THEN 'Carte' WHEN 'f' THEN 'Carte manuscrite' WHEN 'g' THEN 'Vidéo' WHEN 'i' THEN 'Doc sonore non musical' WHEN 'j' THEN 'Doc sonore musical' WHEN 'k' THEN 'Image/Dessin' WHEN 'l' THEN 'Ress. électronique' WHEN 'm' THEN 'Multimédia' WHEN 'r' THEN 'Objet en 3D' ELSE 'Non défini' END

elements.expression: CASE substring(ExtractValue(agkf,'//datafield[@tag="100"]/subfield[@code="a"]'),18,1) WHEN 'a'  THEN 'Jeunesse' WHEN 'b' THEN 'Jeunesse' WHEN 'c' THEN 'Jeunesse' WHEN 'd' THEN 'Jeunesse' WHEN 'e' THEN 'Adulte' WHEN 'k' THEN 'Adulte' WHEN 'm' THEN 'Adulte' WHEN 'u' THEN '~-Inconnu' ELSE '~-Invalide' END
elements.viewExpression: CASE substring(ExtractValue(#agkf,'//datafield[@tag="100"]/subfield[@code="a"]'),18,1) WHEN 'a'  THEN 'Jeunesse' WHEN 'b' THEN 'Jeunesse' WHEN 'c' THEN 'Jeunesse' WHEN 'd' THEN 'Jeunesse' WHEN 'e' THEN 'Adulte' WHEN 'k' THEN 'Adulte' WHEN 'm' THEN 'Adulte' WHEN 'u' THEN '~-Inconnu' ELSE '~-Invalide' END
